Stage 1 database is currently in restricted mode, which is blocking automat=
ion regression runs.
Error: ORA-01035: ORACLE only available to users with RESTRICTED SESSION pr=
ivilege
Impact: Automation regression cannot connect to Stage 1; tests are failing =
due to DB access restrictions.
Request: Please investigate why Stage 1 is in restricted mode and when it w=
ill be returned to normal. Automation will remain blocked until DB access i=
s restored.

